name: Metaword 004 // The Power of Words
description:
Multiple parts of speech may be used

A sentence can be filled with many different parts of speech, however at its core, it will generally adhere to the following rules:

subject + predicate
subject + verb + direct OBJKT

Utility token based on the rules of English Grammar. To be burnt for access to giveaway and limited drops. 

The Rules of Grammar will have an initial run of 6 NFTs. 

If nothing else, it may help you better your command of the Queen's English. Thank you kind sir.
